                                                                 '<br>\r\n<pre><code class="plaintext hljs">[user@testhost ~]$ date\r\nMon Dec 16 13:37:07 UTC 2019\r\n[user@testhost ~]$ date +%s\r\n1576503430\r\n</code></pre><br>',
